task.summary: Started writing code, written an outline to all classes and started writing some functions
Added javadoc comments to whole project
Added functions to get player to add ships to the board
Fixed issues with player number counter, and also placing ships on the board
Added print board method and set to run everytime a ship is placed
Added messages when user enters wrong option when placing ships
Added validation to stop entering a ship position that would go off the board
Fixed issue of not letting you enter a position on the edge of the board
Added numbers printed around the edge of the game board
Tidied up code and split method placeShips into different functions for easier reading
